WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.230
Good morning, family! I'm excited to

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:05.110
be with y'all today. I have

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.070
a pretty strong word from the Lord.

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:09.190
I just got off social

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:12.270
media completely; this word was

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:16.189
so strong. I've had two very strong words

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:18.269
in the last week from the

00:00:18.279 --> 00:00:20.790
Lord. I had one visitation from the

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:23.630
Father, and the presence of the Lord

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:26.230
filled my house so strongly—I can honestly

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:28.269
tell you I've never felt the presence of

00:00:28.279 --> 00:00:32.709
the Lord like that before.

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:37.310
It shook me and gave me a renewed fear

00:00:37.320 --> 00:00:41.510
in Him of how close we are to Jesus

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:44.910
coming. I'm going to start

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:46.270
off with

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:50.510
this: He told me, 'It's time to get

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:52.709
serious. You're not serious

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:55.069
enough; you're not

00:00:55.079 --> 00:00:57.830
pushing and pursuing enough for what's

00:00:57.830 --> 00:00:57.840
coming.'He

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:01.110
said there's a shifting

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:03.670
taking place. It all started while I was

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:06.670
praying over Israel, and He was

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:08.469
speaking to me about the meeting that

00:01:08.479 --> 00:01:10.830
President Biden had with Benjamin

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:13.789
Netanyahu yesterday. He

00:01:13.789 --> 00:01:13.799
said

00:01:13.799 --> 00:01:15.429
there's going to be an

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:18.149
acceleration of times and an

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:20.350
acceleration of things now.

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:22.630
You'll see an acceleration with war,

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:24.230
with

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:26.190
financial stuff, and

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.830
with the signs of the

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.350
heavens—outer

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:32.950
space stuff.

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.149
There's going to be acceleration

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:35.670
with

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.910
the weather and our

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:41.990
atmosphere. He said these are times

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.510
like you've never seen before; the Earth

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:48.550
has never experienced what it's about

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:49.630
to

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:53.190
experience in the coming days. It

00:01:53.190 --> 00:01:53.200
is an

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:55.630
acceleration into unprecedented

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.950
times. We

00:01:57.950 --> 00:01:57.960
have

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:00.429
never in history experienced what

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:02.709
we're about to experience.

00:02:02.709 --> 00:02:02.719
There

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.149
was so much pressure in the Spirit

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:07.510
when He said this. He warned me

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:10.749
about what's coming and

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:12.430
said, 'The body of Christ is

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:14.710
not awake. The people in the

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:18.030
prophetic realm are not

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:18.040
awake.'He

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:19.790
was talking about

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:23.070
coming up higher

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:25.430
and said, 'The level you're

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:28.390
operating in right now is a very shallow

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.270
level. It's time to come up

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:34.550
higher with Me; it's time to separate

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.350
yourself even more than you already

00:02:37.350 --> 00:02:37.360
have.'He

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:40.630
said, 'Brandon, there's a level of

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:42.949
prophetic that the world has

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:44.869
never experienced before,

00:02:44.869 --> 00:02:44.879
and

00:02:44.879 --> 00:02:47.390
you

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:47.400
must

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.790
separate yourself to hear Me

00:02:49.790 --> 00:02:49.800
closely

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:52.110
for what is coming to warn the

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:54.149
people.'He

00:02:54.159 --> 00:02:56.670
said many of His people are

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.750
not hearing

00:02:58.750 --> 00:02:58.760
or

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.229
listening. We are in

00:03:01.239 --> 00:03:04.509
very serious times, for the coming of

00:03:04.509 --> 00:03:04.519
His

00:03:04.519 --> 00:03:08.430
Son is at hand, yet people are asleep. Some

00:03:08.430 --> 00:03:08.440
feel they

00:03:08.440 --> 00:03:10.270
are awake,

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:14.430
but they're still not. He

00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:16.470
was even correcting me,

00:03:16.470 --> 00:03:16.480
saying

00:03:16.480 --> 00:03:18.070
I

00:03:18.070 --> 00:03:18.080
was

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.309
spending

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:23.030
way too much time talking to people on Facebook and answering questions. He

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:24.670
said that's not what

00:03:24.670 --> 00:03:24.680
I'm

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:27.670
here to do; I am to

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:30.509
seek Him, stay at His feet,

00:03:30.519 --> 00:03:32.710
and deliver the word He has for the

00:03:32.720 --> 00:03:35.830
people. It was a rebuke,

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:39.030
so I erased Facebook

00:03:39.030 --> 00:03:39.040
and

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.470
all the things that were a distraction.

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:46.990
I want

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:49.030
to go higher; I don't want to be in

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:50.869
the shallow water. I want to be

00:03:52.959 --> 00:03:55.149
over my head, all the way

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:57.149
to the bottom,

00:03:57.159 --> 00:03:59.429
saturated and controlled

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:02.589
by the Holy Ghost for these last

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:05.149
days. He had me praying for the

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:07.789
tunnels in Israel for the ground

00:04:07.799 --> 00:04:10.350
invasion, and I saw things

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:12.710
plotted against the

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:15.390
soldiers.

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:19.030
The Lord warned

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:22.590
me to pray against booby traps

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:24.390
and

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:26.710
explosives

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.510
rigged

00:04:28.510 --> 00:04:28.520
to

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:30.510
harm

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:34.909
people, including the hostages.

00:04:36.909 --> 00:04:36.919
We

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:40.189
need to intercede for those

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:44.029
people, sending angels

00:04:44.029 --> 00:04:44.039
to

00:04:44.039 --> 00:04:46.710
help because

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:49.150
the enemy is ruthless, without

00:04:49.150 --> 00:04:49.160
a

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:52.430
conscience,

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.629
like

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:56.550
barbarians.

00:04:56.550 --> 00:04:56.560
I

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:58.350
won't

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:02.670
go into a lot

00:05:02.670 --> 00:05:02.680
regarding

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:06.629
the tie

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:10.350
between Israel and the United

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:14.830
States; it's just not smart.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:19.790
This is the

00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:22.070
second part: after He warned me about

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:25.270
the acceleration of war,

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:27.870
times,

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:30.510
finances, and the shift to

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:32.350
cryptocurrencies,

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:37.270
He warned me about 2024

00:05:37.270 --> 00:05:37.280
and

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:42.830
what's coming.

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:49.870
In my prayer time, when

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:51.790
the glory manifested so

00:05:51.790 --> 00:05:51.800
strongly,

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:54.309
He warned me again about coming up

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:57.510
higher.

00:05:59.919 --> 00:06:01.629
It's

00:06:01.639 --> 00:06:03.830
been six days since

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:06.150
my

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:08.309
visitation,

00:06:08.319 --> 00:06:10.710
and He said, 'It's time to come up

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:13.029
higher

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:16.550
in the prophetic realm

00:06:16.550 --> 00:06:16.560
and

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:20.309
in walking with Me, for

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.830
I long for you to abide in

00:06:25.830 --> 00:06:25.840
the fire.'Suddenly,

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:29.430
I saw the heavens

00:06:29.440 --> 00:06:31.870
split above

00:06:31.870 --> 00:06:31.880
me—a

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:35.469
massive

00:06:35.479 --> 00:06:38.990
break in the

00:06:38.990 --> 00:06:39.000
atmosphere—and

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:41.589
I saw the

00:06:41.599 --> 00:06:44.029
Lord seated on His throne, the great God

00:06:44.039 --> 00:06:47.309
Jehovah. I saw this massive

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:50.150
light coming out and Him seated on

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:53.629
His throne. I want you all to

00:06:53.639 --> 00:06:55.309
grasp

00:07:00.350 --> 00:07:00.360
this:

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:09.869
Heaven is

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:16.510
invading Earth now. It's

00:07:16.520 --> 00:07:18.749
an invasion of Heaven on

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:22.189
Earth like we've never seen. I

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:26.990
saw

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:39.710
a liquid lava

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:42.390
flowing out of the throne of God that looked

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:44.350
like liquid honey. It was moving

00:07:44.350 --> 00:07:44.360
slowly

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.550
but

00:07:46.550 --> 00:07:46.560
beautifully,

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.550
with

00:07:48.560 --> 00:07:52.390
sparkles of gold dust

00:07:52.400 --> 00:07:54.950
inside,

00:07:56.960 --> 00:08:00.270
oozing out onto the Earth. It was tiered as I was looking up in the throne room. Then the

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:03.790
Lord allowed me to see inside of

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:06.869
Him. A lot of you

00:08:06.869 --> 00:08:06.879
will

00:08:06.879 --> 00:08:09.230
probably squawk about this, but I really

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:12.430
don't care.

00:08:13.639 --> 00:08:18.469
God is light, and in Him there is no

00:08:18.479 --> 00:08:22.469
darkness at all. He allowed me to

00:08:22.479 --> 00:08:27.189
see the light as His

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:30.230
skin,

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:34.310
and then he allowed my

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:36.870
spiritual eyes

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:40.230
to see inside of

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:43.190
the Father, great El Elyon, the

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:45.389
most high God. I say this with

00:08:45.399 --> 00:08:48.190
fear and reverence:

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:56.870
the light

00:08:56.880 --> 00:08:59.470
is like His skin.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:17.190
Inside Him, He was

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:20.910
endless—His

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:24.030
own dimension.

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:33.750
It looked like a different

00:09:33.760 --> 00:09:36.230
kind of light,

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:39.829
with

00:09:43.110 --> 00:09:43.120
unique

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:48.630
stars

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:51.670
shining all inside of Him.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:58.230
It moved like

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:02.550
it was alive,

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:06.710
transparent and spirit.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:10.949
It had a

00:10:10.959 --> 00:10:12.949
shape and was taking form,

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:14.829
though

00:10:14.839 --> 00:10:18.110
it's

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:22.829
hard to

00:10:22.839 --> 00:10:26.829
explain.

00:10:32.150 --> 00:10:32.160
I

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:41.750
saw

00:10:45.959 --> 00:10:49.870
the silhouette

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:53.509
of His face from afar,

00:10:53.509 --> 00:10:53.519
with

00:10:55.269 --> 00:10:55.279
a

00:10:55.279 --> 00:10:58.350
crown

00:10:58.360 --> 00:11:03.470
on His head.

00:11:03.470 --> 00:11:03.480
Inside

00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:07.670
His head,

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:13.550
I could see three beautiful

00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:16.949
blue

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:19.790
sapphires—huge

00:11:22.430 --> 00:11:22.440
ones.

00:11:24.639 --> 00:11:28.030
All around was

00:11:28.030 --> 00:11:28.040
a

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:31.430
beautiful

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.710
light like

00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:38.629
blue fire,

00:11:38.639 --> 00:11:40.949
making the sapphires

00:11:44.079 --> 00:11:45.670
glow.

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:52.910
Around His face, I could

00:11:52.910 --> 00:11:52.920
only see

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:55.269
His chin

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:57.670
and

00:11:57.680 --> 00:11:59.509
the back of His head;

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:03.190
everything else was fire

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:10.470
radiating a

00:12:10.470 --> 00:12:10.480
captivating

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:15.069
blue

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:20.790
light.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:46.990
I was fixed on

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.350
it;

00:13:01.720 --> 00:13:03.870
I felt like I was melting like

00:13:03.880 --> 00:13:07.030
wax in my home. It

00:13:22.839 --> 00:13:25.670
was the most holy moment,

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:29.750
seeing

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:33.389
a glimpse of

00:13:46.199 --> 00:13:49.590
the silhouette of the

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:52.910
Father.

00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:55.790
Then

00:13:57.389 --> 00:13:57.399
He

00:14:00.150 --> 00:14:00.160
said,

00:14:01.839 --> 00:14:04.470
'Focus and

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:05.910
see this wall.'Upon

00:14:05.910 --> 00:14:05.920
the

00:14:05.920 --> 00:14:08.590
wall was

00:14:08.590 --> 00:14:08.600
ancient text,

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:12.230
eons of

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:15.509
time, with angelic writing

00:14:33.759 --> 00:14:37.310
engraved into stone

00:14:37.310 --> 00:14:37.320
with

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:41.310
fire.

00:14:51.800 --> 00:14:55.749
This was writing on a

00:14:55.759 --> 00:14:59.590
granite rock with

00:14:59.590 --> 00:14:59.600
triangles,

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:01.790
circles,

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.870
waves,

00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:11.389
and squares.

00:15:11.399 --> 00:15:12.990
He told me it was

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:16.069
an ancient text etched

00:15:16.069 --> 00:15:16.079
in

00:15:16.079 --> 00:15:17.269
for millions of years.

00:15:21.079 --> 00:15:23.350
I still

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:24.790
don't have the full revelation of why He

00:15:24.800 --> 00:15:27.470
showed me this,

00:15:27.470 --> 00:15:27.480
but

00:15:27.480 --> 00:15:30.509
it was

00:15:56.240 --> 00:15:59.189
being downloaded like

00:15:59.199 --> 00:16:01.150
a

00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:03.749
fire hydrant.

00:16:11.920 --> 00:16:14.629
He said,

00:16:14.639 --> 00:16:18.230
'My prophetic people

00:16:18.240 --> 00:16:21.350
are thinking too carnal;

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:24.670
it's time to come up

00:16:24.680 --> 00:16:26.230
another level.'He even told

00:16:26.230 --> 00:16:26.240
me my

00:16:26.240 --> 00:16:28.230
thinking

00:16:28.230 --> 00:16:28.240
was

00:16:28.240 --> 00:16:31.710
too shallow.

00:16:31.710 --> 00:16:31.720
He

00:16:31.720 --> 00:16:34.269
asked,

00:16:34.279 --> 00:16:35.629
'Do you know the difference

00:16:35.639 --> 00:16:38.269
between a flash in the pan and someone who stands the test of time?'He told me not to be a flash in the pan but a pillar who

00:16:45.710 --> 00:16:45.720
teaches

00:16:54.560 --> 00:16:57.829
the word. He

00:16:57.839 --> 00:16:59.870
brought up brother Kenneth Hagin,

00:16:59.870 --> 00:16:59.880
saying

00:16:59.880 --> 00:17:02.629
brother Hagin didn't just give a

00:17:02.639 --> 00:17:05.390
word of the day;

00:17:13.039 --> 00:17:15.909
he taught the people how

00:17:15.919 --> 00:17:18.669
to live by faith

00:17:18.669 --> 00:17:18.679
and

00:17:18.679 --> 00:17:21.230
stand on the covenant.

00:17:23.360 --> 00:17:25.429
To stand the test of time,

00:17:25.439 --> 00:17:28.230
you must teach the

00:17:28.240 --> 00:17:29.630
word.

00:17:32.320 --> 00:17:34.390
Too many prophetic

00:17:34.400 --> 00:17:37.950
people are just a flash in the pan and will burn out.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:40.990
It's about getting in the word

00:17:40.990 --> 00:17:41.000
and

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:42.590
teaching the

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:45.029
people how to pray.

00:17:45.039 --> 00:17:47.430
He said, 'When you

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:50.350
seek Me daily and

00:17:50.350 --> 00:17:50.360
come

00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:52.150
out of carnal thinking,

00:17:54.750 --> 00:17:54.760
I

00:17:56.919 --> 00:17:59.029
will

00:17:59.039 --> 00:18:02.070
give you those words.'We are

00:18:02.070 --> 00:18:02.080
in a

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:05.230
season

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:15.029
of great birthing pains,

00:18:15.039 --> 00:18:17.310
more than ever before. What we've

00:18:18.960 --> 00:18:20.950
experienced

00:18:20.950 --> 00:18:20.960
is

00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:22.750
nothing compared to what is about to

00:18:22.760 --> 00:18:26.029
happen. He said this

